      "content": "I see. So, even if we consider the downsides for competitiveness, you seem to be saying that the risk of catastrophe is a much more certain or serious priority than the risk of losing the tech race. Are you saying that the 'existential risk' argument is actually the more objective or scientifically sound position to take here?",
